Assignment 8: Phân vùng ảnh (Image Segmentation)¶

Tng quan: bi tp ny chng ta s luyn tp thut ton phn vng nh s dng K-Means v Mean Shift. Cc bi tp trong phn ny yu cu bn s dng cc khng gian c trng khc nhau biu din cc im nh, sau s dng K-Means v Mean Shift c sn trong th vin sklearn phn vng nh

In [1]:
import warnings
warnings.filterwarnings("ignore")

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import cv2
import numpy as np
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
from sklearn.cluster import MeanShift

Câu hỏi 1: Phân vùng ảnh xám¶

phn ny ta s biu din mi im nh bng mt vecto 1 chiu (khng gian c trng 1D): gi tr sng ti im nh tng ng

In [2]:
img = cv2.imread('img1.jpg')
print(img.shape)
img = cv2.cvtColor(img, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)
print(img.shape)

plt.imshow(img, cmap='gray')
plt.show()

(183, 275, 3)
(183, 275)

Xy dng ma trn biu din d liu:

In [3]:
X = img.reshape((-1, 1))
print(X.shape)

(50325, 1)

Lc ny mi hng ca ma trn X tng ng vi mt vector biu din mt im nh trn nh ban u. Ta s th s dng thut ton K-Means v MeanShift phn vng cc im nh theo sng ca n:

  • KMeans
In [4]:
kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=10, init='random').fit(X)
print(kmeans)
center = kmeans.cluster_centers_
label = kmeans.labels_

print(center)
print(label.shape)

segmented_image = center[label]
segmented_image = np.reshape(segmented_image, img.shape)
plt.imshow(segmented_image, cmap='gray')
plt.show()

  • MeanShift: i vi MeanShift, ta cn mt hm khi to ngu nhin cc ht seed:
In [5]:
def init_seed(X, k):
    return X[np.random.choice(X.shape[0], k, replace=False)]
In [6]:
random_seeds = init_seed(X, 10)

ms = MeanShift(bandwidth=1, seeds=random_seeds)
print(ms)
ms.fit(X)
center = ms.cluster_centers_
label = ms.labels_

print(center)
print(label.shape)

segmented_image = center[label]
segmented_image = np.reshape(segmented_image, img.shape)
plt.imshow(segmented_image/255.0, cmap='gray')
plt.show()
